00:25:35,270 --> 00:25:38,600
 Why does he have a pot on his head?

212
00:25:41,150 --> 00:25:44,290
 But it's still pretty cute! Thank you.

213
00:25:44,290 --> 00:25:47,170
 You've worked hard. You can do it!

