00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:14,500
The project everyone sees here comes from Cai Niao Posting Station.

216
00:26:14,500 --> 00:26:17,500
According to Cai Niao Posting Station's logo designer,

217
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:20,000
the inspiration for this design originated from themself.

218
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:22,870
Because sometimes, when getting off work late and the number of express deliveries piled up,

219
00:26:22,870 --> 00:26:26,180
